#################################################################

###  http://purl.org/dc/terms/available
<http://purl.org/dc/terms/available> owl:equivalentProperty <https://w3id.org/ontometal#releaseYear> ;
                                     rdfs:subPropertyOf <http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> .


###  https://w3id.org/ontometal#bandID
<https://w3id.org/ontometal#bandID> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
